                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding>
                        <p>
                           <hi rend="smallcaps">housing</hi> The last item in an envelope of fragments from the
                           <persName key="person_9878742" role="formerOwner">Allestree</persName> collection, mainly removed from volumes in his collection apparently by
                Thomas Vere Bayne (see no. 28, though that item appears to be in the handwriting of
                William Wake), but also including letters to Allestree. Apart from this fragment,
                others are post-1600, apart from a former flyleaf from a glossed printed book of
                canon law. This would appear to have been a flyleaf in an octavo printed book. </p>
                     </binding>
